WHAT IS IT?
-----------

  'KouQuad' is a Workbench game where you have to move coloured
tiles by clicking on 'Quads' -which are large tiles containing 4
small coloured tiles- so tiles of the same colour are placed next
to each other. The more tiles of the same type there are, the more
points you get...

  A feature of the game is the 'fall and move tiles' option. You
can use this option to force the remaining tiles to fall toward
the bottom, and then these tiles will be moved toward the left on
the board. If tiles of the same colour are next to each other,
they will disappear. If any tile remain, the game ends, otherwise,
the game continues and it will display a new board...

  Have fun!

